character - 8 bits (must be a printable ascii character no bigger than 127
fg color - 4 bits (16 colors)
bg color - 4 bits (16 colors)
each cell occupies 2 bytes of space
a 80x24 image, uncompressed, is about 2 kb
in absolute worst case, if we had a mega big image (240x72) it would still take
up less than a megabyte:
